Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:08.04,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.96,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:16.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:21.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.89,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.56,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:30.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:36.32,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.45,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.20,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.62,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.75,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 時間 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:54.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前煩惱的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:02:00.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}來展開新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:05.52,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做夢嗎？現在的夢還不能說！
