Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.02,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.11,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎樣的天氣 I need you!!
